text: Maofelis cantonensis is an extinct basal nimravid from Late Eocene-aged Youganwo Formation of Maoming Basin, Guangdong Province, China. ==References== Category:Prehistoric mammals of Asia Category:Nimravidae Category:Eocene carnivorans Category:Fossil taxa described in 2016 Category:Paleontology in Guangdong
title: Maofelis
